| Element | Requirement |
|---|---|
| Board | Hidden |
| Timer | Paused |
| Resume button | Visible |
| Menu | Optional |

## 12.4 Completion screen

| Element | Requirement |
|---|---|
| Success message | Required |
| Difficulty | Required |
| Final time | Required |
